BTTTriggers.BTTInlineAppleScript: if application "Google Play Music Desktop Player" is running then	set gpdmp_status to do shell script "GPMDP_AUTH_KEY=76016fea-ac4e-445b-83e1-2919306e389 /Users/gavinw/Go/bin/gpmdp status"	if gpdmp_status is "Playback paused" then		do shell script "GPMDP_AUTH_KEY=76016fea-ac4e-445b-83e1-2919306e389 /Users/gavinw/Go/bin/gpmdp play"	else		do shell script "GPMDP_AUTH_KEY=76016fea-ac4e-445b-83e1-2919306e389 /Users/gavinw/Go/bin/gpmdp pause"	end ifend if

BTTTriggerConfig.BTTTouchBarAppleScriptString: if application "Google Play Music Desktop Player" is running then	tell application "Google Play Music Desktop Player"		if player state is playing then return "pause"	end tellend ifreturn "play"
